text: Jorge Luis Álvarez Galvez (born 5 April 1959) is a Cuban rower. He competed in two events at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Cuba Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Pan American Games medalists in rowing Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Cuba Category:Rowers at the 1979 Pan American Games
